data.description: MLS# 273155 Immaculate Home in South Richland located near Claybell Park and Amon Creek Elementary!  You will love this home located in the Cottages at Clearwater Creek.  Absolutely PERFECT! Awesome Kitchen with plenty of  counter space and Stainless appliances! Vaulted Ceilings in the Dining Room and Living Room giving this home a spacious feel!  The Master Bed has 2 closets!  The Master Bath features a dual vanity! Bedrooms 2 and  3 share a full bath.  Bedroom 2 has a walk in closet!  OVERSIZED Garage with a 4 foot extension!  COVERED PATIO!  Back yard faces East to avoid the afternoon sun! Fully Fenced yard!  This one has it all!
